description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 50, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 250, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Leverage for East, 5 for South, and 5 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50505-16552-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [250 Votes, Top 5% Score]
